-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nsv1665703005961.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nsv1665703005961.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nsv1665703005961.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nsv1665703005961\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $foreign\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"nsv1665703005961___foreign_266370\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return a boolean value that indicates whether the entity is an Up entity in the component structure.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__topic_d83768e1_d83769e1_d83770e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__p_d83771e1_d83772e1_d83773e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$foreign</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__topic_d55397e1_d55398e1_d55399e1_d55400e1_d55401e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179831e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__d6092e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__d6092e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__d6092e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__d6092e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__d6092e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__d6092e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__d6092e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name; optional. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__topic_d55402e1_d55403e1_d55404e1_d55405e1_d55406e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179831e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$foreign</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is painted as an up (foreign) entity.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is not painted as an up entity.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8657e1_d8658e1_d8659e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n An error occurred\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__p_d83780e1_d83781e1_d83782e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8660e1_d8661e1_d8662e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$foreign</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8660e1_d8661e1_d8662e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8660e1_d8661e1_d8662e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8660e1_d8661e1_d8662e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8660e1_d8661e1_d8662e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8660e1_d8661e1_d8662e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665703005961__table_d8660e1_d8661e1_d8662e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__topic_d55407e1_d55408e1_d55409e1_d55410e1_d55411e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179831e268\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__d6049e20\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__topic_d55412e1_d55413e1_d55414e1_d55415e1_d55416e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179831e278\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__p_d83792e1_d83793e1_d83794e1\">An Up entity is an inner entity that represents the one side in a one-to-many relationship with the outer entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__p_d83795e1_d83796e1_d83797e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$foreign</span> function is useful in the read trigger of a modeled entity, because it allows you to determine at runtime how the entity is placed in the component structure.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__section_y2t_vnz_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d179831e293\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$foreign</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$foreign</span> function can be used in read triggers\n               of modeled entities to specify different actions depending on how the entity is\n               painted on the form.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, if the entity is not painted as an up\n               entity, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">u_where</span> clause ensures that all the occurrences where\n               EXPIRATION_DATE is today or later are read.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">If the entity is painted as an up entity, the unqualified\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">read</span> statement ensures that only the single matching occurrence\n               is read.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"nsv1665703005961__pre_rld_wnz_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; trigger: Read\nif ($foreign = 0)\n read u_where (EXPIRATION_DATE &gt;= $date)\nelse\n read\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvq1665702552959.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>read</a><p>Set the access mode.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ffb1665702661430.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>u_where</a><p>Provide a DBMS-independent profile for selection with read and selectdb.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530414\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530414\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$foreign Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $foreign Return a boolean value that indicates whether the entity is an Up entity in the component structure. $foreign { ( Entity ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name; optional. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by $foreign Value Meaning 1 Entity is painted as an up (foreign) entity. 0 Entity is not painted as an up entity. \"\" An error occurred If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $foreign Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description An Up entity is an inner entity that represents the one side in a one-to-many relationship with the outer entity. The $foreign function is useful in the read trigger of a modeled entity, because it allows you to determine at runtime how the entity is placed in the component structure. Example: Using $foreign The $foreign function can be used in read triggers of modeled entities to specify different actions depending on how the entity is painted on the form. In the following example, if the entity is not painted as an up entity, the u_where clause ensures that all the occurrences where EXPIRATION_DATE is today or later are read. If the entity is painted as an up entity, the unqualified read statement ensures that only the single matching occurrence is read. ; trigger: Read if ($foreign = 0) read u_where (EXPIRATION_DATE >= $date) else read endif Copy Related Links read Set the access mode. u_where Provide a DBMS-independent profile for selection with read and selectdb. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}